name: Yeb Yeb Adem'thorn
Lore: 'Senator who opposes the taxation of trade routes. Some say that a recent move from his homeworld to a luxurious Coruscant abode is evidence of his corruption.',
Text: 'Agendas: trade, wealth. While in a senate majority, once during your turn, may peek at top card of opponent''s Reserve Deck; return that card or lose 1 Force to make it lost.',
